These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-1::.
There 2 different types of food: grapes, raspberry
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating raspberry and the person driving the ship have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |
| Food    | raspberry | grapes  |
| Sport   | ship    | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk
House: gothic-revival, modern
1. the person drinking 7up and the gothic-revival house have the same parity positions##9
2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |     2     |
| Beverage   | milk      | 7up       |
| Food       | modern | gothic-revival |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, collecting
1. the fan folk and the person who's hobby is singing have different parity positions##9
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | folk       |
| Sport         | singing | collecting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-9-4::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: white, aquamarine
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: parkour, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
2. the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's sport is swimming have different parity positions##9
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Nationality   | aquamarine | white |
| Sport         | parkour | swimming  |

 #################################

 
